                        "username": "geissonator"
                    },
                    "message": "Not sure what's going on here but the obmc-host-shutdown@.target is meant to be a graceful shutdown. You just need to install the graceful service for your system in it. For example on IBM systems we put pldmSoftPowerOff.service and xyz.openbmc_project.Ipmi.Internal.SoftPowerOff.service in it to allow the pldm and ipmi inband services to notify the host to shutdown."
                },
