                        "username": "DelphineCCChiu"
                    },
                    "message": "Both shutdown and graceful-shutdown target will be implemented in our project\nI add the request transition type for graceful-shutdown in phosphor-dbus-interfaces , the code build will be pass after that commit merged:\n\nhttps://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/phosphor-dbus-interfaces/+/60168"
                },
